<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="787" height="396" viewBox="0 0 787 396"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="white"/><rect x="20" y="16" width="80" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="60" y="37" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">A</text><rect x="120" y="16" width="80" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="160" y="37" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">B</text><line x1="60" y1="48" x2="60" y2="348" stroke="#555" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="6 4"/><line x1="160" y1="48" x2="160" y2="348" stroke="#555" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="6 4"/><rect x="16" y="156" width="730" height="56" rx="2" ry="2" fill="#eef6ff" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><polygon points="16,156 48,156 48,170 42,176 16,176" fill="#eef6ff" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><text x="22" y="170" font-family="monospace" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#111">ref</text><text x="24" y="188" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">External dependency handshake with a very long descriptive line that previously escaped the ref block.</text><text x="24" y="204" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">Return payload includes another long descriptive line to stress multiline measurement.</text><rect x="20" y="240" width="751" height="84" rx="2" ry="2" fill="#fafafa" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><polygon points="20,240 767,240 767,254 761,260 20,260" fill="#fafafa" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1"/><text x="28" y="254" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" font-weight="600" fill="#111">group This group label is intentionally verbose so the container width follows measured content correctly</text><line x1="60" y1="80" x2="160" y2="80" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="160,80 152,75 152,85" fill="#111" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="68" y="72" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">kickoff</text><line x1="60" y1="276" x2="160" y2="276" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="160,276 152,271 152,281" fill="#111" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="68" y="268" text-anchor="start" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">work</text><path d="M20,100 H705 L719 114 V144 H20 Z" fill="#fff8c4" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M705 100 V114 H719" fill="none" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="28" y="120" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">This is a very long yellow note line that should force the container to grow wider than defaults.</text><text x="28" y="136" font-family="monospace" font-size="12" fill="#111">And this second line keeps the multiline height constraints honest.</text><rect x="20" y="348" width="80" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="60" y="369" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">A</text><rect x="120" y="348" width="80" height="32" rx="4" ry="4" fill="#f6f6f6" stroke="#111" stroke-width="1"/><text x="160" y="369" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace" font-size="13" fill="#111111">B</text></svg>
